title: Felipe del Mestre
text: Felipe del Mestre (born 25 September 1993) is an <a href="Argentines">Argentine</a> <a href="rugby%20union">rugby union</a> player. He plays <a href="rugby%20sevens">rugby sevens</a> for . He has medaled at the 2019 <a href="Pan%20American%20Games">Pan American Games</a>. He was also selected to Argentina squad to compete at the <a href="2020%20Summer%20Olympics">2020 Summer Olympics</a> in the <a href="Rugby%20sevens%20at%20the%202020%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%20tournament">men's rugby sevens tournament</a>.
